title: The Twilight Zone Episode 23- A world of difference
description:
Arthur Curtis is a businessman. One day, he finds his phone no longer works, and is surprised to hear a voice yell, "Cut!" Suddenly he is faced with the fact that his office was actually a set on a soundstage. He is told that "Arthur Curtis" is merely a role he was playing, and that his real name is Jerry Raigan, a declining movie star. He tries to find Arthur Curtis&#039;s house, but cannot find any evidence of it; Raigan&#039;s agent tells him that the show with Arthur Curtis in it is being canceled because they believe he has had a nervous breakdown. Raigan/Curtis rushes back to the set, which is being dismantled, and demands not to be left in the uncaring world of Jerry Raigan. Raigan&#039;s agent shows up on the set to find Curtis/Raigan has vanished.
